      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I'm listing my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it's a total showstopper! This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014I've babied it since the day I got it, keeping it garaged and spotless. It looks and drives like it just left the showroom floor! If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for with zero compromises, this is the one. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast with it. Drop me a message if you want to come see this beauty in person!",
