    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a definitive example of the E46 chassis. This vehicle features the legendary S54 inline-six power plant, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated VANOS system. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Chassis integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension retains its factory-correct damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection. Finished in pristine Laguna Seca Blue over Nappa leather, every seal, gasket, and mechanical component reflects a rigorous maintenance schedule. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
